{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3b9a682714","title":"您，毛泽东同志，可以领导谈判","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a35b0437f8","index":0,"year":1951,"month":6,"day":30,"articleId":"3b9a682714"}],"tags":[{"id":"625c516d2c","name":"朝鲜战争","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"ae0a6697a5","name":"彭德怀","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","name":"斯大林选集（诸夏怀斯社2017年5月）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"斯大林，诸夏怀斯社2017年5月","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives5/main/d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"1332d101b8","name":"斯大林"}]},"publication_details":{"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"89d765d50c","type":"paragraph","text":"您，毛泽东同志，可以领导谈判","index":0,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"3b9a682714"},{"id":"80eca27781","type":"paragraph","text":"一一致毛泽东电","index":1,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"3b9a682714"},{"id":"cb6c9af87b","type":"paragraph","text":"（1951年6月30日）","index":2,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"3b9a682714"},{"id":"6584d8ceaa","type":"paragraph","text":"北京致克拉索夫斯基转毛泽东同志：","index":3,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"3b9a682714"},{"id":"658099de83","type":"paragraph","text":"您关于停战谈判问题的电报收到了。","index":4,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"3b9a682714"},{"id":"c9e93c2dd7","type":"paragraph","text":"我们认为，应立即通过广播答复季奇微，同意与其代表进行关于停战谈判的会唔。这个协定应由朝鲜人民军总司令和中国志愿军司令员，也就是金日成和彭德怀签署。如果没有中国志愿军司令员签署，那么，美国人会认为朝鲜单方面的签字不具有任何意义。应坚决拒绝把元山地区的丹麦医疗船作为会唔地点，应要求在三八线的开城地区举行会暗。止如您指出的，现在您掌握着停战的主动权，所以美国人将不得不在会唔地点的问题上做出让步。","index":5,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"3b9a682714"},{"id":"cf2cd71a18","type":"paragraph","text":"您今天要给季奇微发出大致如下的答复：","index":6,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"3b9a682714"},{"id":"68d274f40b","type":"paragraph","text":"“致联合国军总司令季奇微将军：","index":7,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"3b9a682714"},{"id":"f273b61687","type":"paragraph","text":"您28日U关于谈判停战的声明收到了。我们受命向您声明，同意与您的代表会唔，以进行停止军事行动和确立停战的谈判。我们建议以三八线的开城地区作为会唔地点。如果您同意，我们的代表准备在7月10-15日同您的代表会唔","index":8,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"3b9a682714"},{"id":"fc8cdb51b6","type":"paragraph","text":"朝鲜人民军总司令金日成","index":9,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"3b9a682714"},{"id":"1107ac4faa","type":"paragraph","text":"中国人民志愿军司令员彭德怀”","index":10,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"3b9a682714"},{"id":"c6ef6c0ccb","type":"paragraph","text":"在电报中，您建议从莫斯科派人去领导停战谈判，当然，这是不","index":11,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"3b9a682714"},{"id":"4aebade7cf","type":"paragraph","text":"1这里指的是北京时间，按美国东部时间，该声明是29日发表的需要的，也是毫无意义的。您，毛泽东同志，可以领导谈判。最多，我们可以在某些问题上提一些建议。我们也不能和金日成保持直接的联系。您应该同他联系。","index":12,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"3b9a682714"},{"id":"b01a18d5df","type":"paragraph","text":"菲利波夫","index":13,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"3b9a682714"},{"id":"df136a4257","type":"paragraph","text":"第335号密码电报","index":14,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"3b9a682714"},{"id":"e537880f08","type":"paragraph","text":"1951年6月30日《朝鲜战争：俄国档案馆的解密文件》","index":15,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"3b9a682714"},{"id":"9cf8d50e3c","type":"paragraph","text":"选自新编《斯大林全集》（中册）第839页","index":16,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"3b9a682714"},{"id":"3832e803e8","type":"paragraph","text":"档案附卷九第143-144页","index":17,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"3b9a682714"}],"page":{"id":"50378c45ec","publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"3b9a682714","start":2751,"end":2752}}}},"__N_SSG":true}